<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7666494>
    dc:description "Figs 41–54. Afraustraloxenodes hulleyi sp. n. 41–43. Paratype, adult male; 41. Head and collum, dorsal view. 42. Sensilla of articles VI of left antenna. 43. Distal part of crooked trichomes. 44–52. Holotype female. 44. Right antenna. 45–46. Sensilla of articles VII and VI of the same antenna. 47. Labrum, only part of cuticular setae shown. 48. Distal part of crooked trichome. 49. Seta on prefemur of right leg I. 50. Seta on coxa of left leg III. 51–52. Right telotarsi IV and VI, anterior view. 53–54.Adult male from Kowie River mouth, sensilla of articles VII and VI of left antenna. Scale bars: Figs 41, 43, 44 = 50 m; other figures = 25 m." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7666494/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

